*DESCRIPTION_START
Knee-deep in the grass at the top of the sandy hill you can see the entire
surface of the small island quite clearly. To the south there is nothing to
see except sand and seawater, but down the gentler north slope you see a
thicket of small, twisted trees of some kind.
