NUMBER 3256
NAME Crescent isle, twisted wood
DAY_LIGHT
FOREST
REGION 11
MONSTER_GROUP 107
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The trees which grow in the salt air here are twisted things, each trunk
as narrow as your arm and no hunched form taller than human height. Sparse
needles, brilliant green and studded with an occasional spring bud, cling
for their lives to the rough-barked branches.
*DESCRIPTION_END
