DAY_LIGHT
FOREST
REGION 11
MONSTER_GROUP 107
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Two of the shrivelled trees here have grown into a single shape, their
trunks twisting around each other to form a gnarled pillar of springy
wood. Neither has many branches anywhere save at their very ends, where
the double-sized spreading canopy reaches an unusual
height for this thicket.
*DESCRIPTION_END
