NUMBER 3258
NAME Crescent isle, twisted wood
DAY_LIGHT
FOREST
REGION 11
MONSTER_GROUP 107
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
For the briefest of moments your breath catches in your throat... someone is
watching you from behind the nearest tree! Then you realize that it is just
another of the sickly plants, doubled over by wind and the poor soil. A knot
sticking out of the trunk has a shape vaguely resembling a hooded face,
explaining your moment of panic.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 3257
