*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The face looks almost familiar, though the effect seems to come from the general anonymity of its features more than any specific trait. Only its apparent hostility marks it, and you have seen more hostility in your adventuring career than many.
*DESCRIPTION_END
