NAME Crescent isle, sandgrass
DAY_LIGHT
FOREST
REGION 11
MONSTER_GROUP 107
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The clumps of sand have gathered here into a single low shape, a shelf of
sorts which buttresses the edge of a narrow length of beach. As with the
vegetation on the rest of the island, it serves as an ineffective barrier
against any traveller larger than a kobold child. The grass grows thicker
than ever, everywhere except the shelf itself.
*DESCRIPTION_END
