NUMBER 3281
NAME Sandy cave
CAVE
DARKNESS
MONSTER_GROUP 87
REGION 11
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The floor of this cave is damp sand, smelling faintly of salt. Trickles of
water flow along the walls, either condensation or run-off from the ground
above, adding moisture to the granular soil even as it evaporates into the
humid air. The cave is like a tunnel here, leading down and south, staying
directly under the island proper.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 413
EXIT S 3282
