;
NUMBER 3282
NAME Sandy cave
CAVE
DARKNESS
MONSTER_GROUP 87
REGION 11
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Dropping more sharply as it moves away from the cave entrance, the floor is
still covered in a fine layer of sand. Fingers of limestone discoloration
and tiny stalactites line the walls and ceiling, none of them large or fully
developed. The caves have only been here for a short time, compared to the
older, larger ones you have seen, and dripping water has not had time to form
impressive formations as yet. In a way, you can appreciate this, as it gives
anything lurking in this particular darkness nowhere to hide.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 413
EXIT N 3281
